div.mdc-layout-grid
	div.mdc-layout-grid__inner
		div.mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-2-desktop
		div.mdc-card.mdc-layout-grid__cell.mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-8
			section.mdc-card__media(style="background-image: url('img/logo.png');background-size: contain; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 80px; margin: 16px")
			section(style="padding: 16px")
				| Databox lets you take control of your personal data and IoT devices. See the&nbsp;
				a(href="https://github.com/me-box/databox")
					| documentation
				| &nbsp;for help in setting up a Databox.

			section(style="padding: 16px")
				div.mdc-text-field(style="width: 100%")
					input#loginField.mdc-text-field__input(type='url', style="width: 100%", required=true)
					label.mdc-floating-label(for='loginField')
						| Databox Password
					div.mdc-line-ripple

			section.mdc-card__actions
				button#loginButton.mdc-card__action.mdc-button.mdc-button--primary(disabled)
					| Login
